               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the first four months of the year (fols. 2ra-253v)&#xD;
I-1) Maskaram (fols. 2ra-63rc)&#xD;
I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 64ra-117vc)&#xD;
I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 118ra-180vc) &#xD;
I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols. 181ra-253vc)&#xD;
The commemoration notes are followed by ʿarke-hymns&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
